OL,3,CCouncil finance boss given #400k
OL,4,Credundancy payout
OL,6,FA senior Newcastle City Council
OL,7,Ffinance boss was given a payout of
OL,8,Fmore than #400,000 when his role was
OL,9,Faxed in 2022.
OL,11,FTony Kirkham was made redundant in a
OL,12,Fshakeup of Newcastle City Council
OL,13,Fbosses and has now been named as one
OL,14,Fof the highest remunerated council
OL,15,Fofficials in the country.
OL,17,FThe former director of resources
OL,18,Freceived #496,403 in 2022-23 in
OL,19,Fsalary, compensation and pension
OL,20,Fbenefits - the third most of any
OL,21,Fcouncil employee in the UK.
