OL,3,CCouncil finance boss given #400k
OL,4,Credundancy payout
OL,6,FThe figure was mostly made up of a
OL,7,F#419,184 compensation package after
OL,8,Fhis #148,000-a-year post was scrapped
OL,9,Fin July 2022. It was the biggest pay-
OL,10,Foff for loss of office recorded by any
OL,11,Fcouncil that year.
OL,13,FIn the months prior, Mr Kirkham had
OL,14,Fbeen due to depart his role of his own
OL,15,Faccord after accepting a similar job
OL,16,Fin his home city of Nottingham.
