OL,3,CCouncil finance boss given #400k
OL,4,Credundancy payout
OL,6,FBut that offer was later withdrawn and
OL,7,Fhe was ultimately made redundant
OL,8,Finstead, at what was a time of major
OL,9,Fupheaval at the civic centre following
OL,10,Fthe departure of previous chief
OL,11,Fexecutive Pat Ritchie, council leader
OL,12,FNick Forbes, and a number of other
OL,13,Fsenior figures.
OL,15,FCurrent chief executive Pam Smith said
OL,16,Fat the time that the restructure was
OL,17,Fneeded to "make significant ongoing
OL,18,Fsavings" that totalled #320,000 per
OL,19,Fyear.
