OL,6,FBut Colin Ferguson, leader of the
OL,7,Fcouncil's Lib Dem opposition, called
OL,8,Fthe payout "beyond shocking" on Monday
OL,9,F8 April and questioned whether it was
OL,10,F"good value for money" at a time when
OL,11,Fthe council is facing tens of millions
OL,12,Fof pounds worth of budget cuts.
OL,14,FHe added: "When the director of
OL,15,Fresources role was made redundant, it
OL,16,Fwas claimed that this would contribute
OL,17,Fto #320,000 a year in staffing savings
OL,18,F(alongside the deletion of another
OL,19,Frole).
