OL,6,F"The payout, over and above standard
OL,7,Fsalary, comfortably exceeds this sum.
OL,8,FWe want to know: how long will it take
OL,9,Ffor this move to break even?
OL,11,F"Put into context, the payout is
OL,12,Flarger than roughly two thirds of the
OL,13,Findividual savings proposals put
OL,14,Fforward by Labour in their budget in
OL,15,FMarch.
