OL,6,F"It's larger than either the slashing
OL,7,Fof the supporting independence scheme
OL,8,For the axing of the discretionary
OL,9,Fcrisis support scheme, both of which
OL,10,Fthe Lib Dems opposed. It can't be
OL,11,Fdismissed as trivial."
