OL,7,F"Constitutional Committee agreed a
OL,8,Fnumber of senior management changes
OL,9,Fincluding the deletion of the director
OL,10,Fof resources post in June 2022 as part
OL,11,Fof wider changes to realign the senior
OL,12,Fmanagement team and to cut costs. The
OL,13,Fdirector of resources was made
OL,14,Fredundant and left the council on July
OL,15,F31, 2022.
